sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant Client as Client Frontend
    participant AS as Serveur d'Autorisation
    participant RS as Serveur de Ressources

    User->>Browser: 1. Initie un virement 650 EUR vers Dupont Jean
    Browser->>Client: 2. Transmet l'action utilisateur

    Client->>AS: 3. POST /as/par RFC 9126 - authorization_details RAR<br/>type: payment_initiation, montant: 650 EUR, creditorIban: FR7612345600012345678901

    AS-->>Client: 4. { request_uri: urn:...XYZ, expires_in: 60 }

    Client->>Browser: 5. Redirect /authorize?client_id=lbp&request_uri=urn:...XYZ

    Browser->>AS: 6. GET /authorize
    AS->>AS: 7. Recupere les authorization_details depuis request_uri

    AS->>Browser: 8. Affiche la page de consentement - Beneficiaire: Dupont Jean - IBAN: FR76...8901 - Montant: 650 EUR
    Note over AS,Browser: Affichage des details AVANT la SCA obligatoire Art.5 RTS DSP2

    AS->>AS: 9. Dynamic Linking: OTP = HMAC(cle_user, 65000 || FR7612345600012345678901 || 20240315)
    Note over AS: OTP genere et lie a ce paiement specifique AVANT envoi a l'utilisateur

    AS->>User: 10. Envoi OTP lie aux details du paiement par SMS ou notification push

    User->>AS: 11. Saisit et soumet l'OTP sur la page de consentement

    AS->>AS: 12. Verification: HMAC(cle_user, 65000 || FR7612345600012345678901 || 20240315) == OTP soumis
    Note over AS: Si montant ou IBAN modifie - le HMAC ne correspond pas - paiement rejete

    AS-->>Browser: 13. Redirect callback?code=CODE&state=S&iss=https://as.lbp.fr
    Browser->>Client: 14. Retourne le code d'autorisation

    Client->>AS: 15. POST /token { code, code_verifier, DPoP-Proof RFC 9449 }
    AS-->>Client: 16. { access_token DPoP-bound, token_type: DPoP }

    Client->>RS: 17. POST /payments - Authorization: DPoP access_token - Body: { creditorIban, montant, remittanceInfo }

    RS->>RS: 18. Valide le DPoP binding - verifie authorization_details == body
    RS-->>Client: 19. { paymentId: PAY-2024-LBP-001, status: AcceptedSettlementInProcess }

    Client->>Browser: 20. Affiche la confirmation du virement
    Browser-->>User: 21. Virement confirme - 650 EUR - Loye
